description: Mom and Dad are going out./Caillou and his family go to a theme park./Caillou doesn't go to school./It's the first time Caillou is going to spend the night away from his home./Poor Caillou! He's fallen off his bike and scraped his knee.

title: Plays Baby/Flies on a Plane/In the Bathtub/Goes Birdwatching/The Doll
description: Caillou thinks his sister Rosie is getting favorable treatment./It's Caillou's first flight./It's bathtime, and for Caillou that means trouble./Grandma always has the best surprises./Mom is putting on her makeup to go out with Dad.

title: Caillou's Gym Day/Our Rocket Ship/Caillou Helps Grandpa/The Backyard Bowlers/Caillou's Milk Run
description: Caillou gets a special invitation to go to André's gym class./Caillou and Leo are playing with their rocket ships in the park./On a winter day, Dad and Caillou go over to Grandpa's with their skates./When Caillou and Rosie stay at Grandma and Grandpa's house, Grandpa uses pop bottles and a rubber ball to create a kid's bowling alley./Caillou accidentally spills the rest of the milk before Rosie could get her cereal.

title: Caillou the Santa Helper
description: Caillou helps Santa deliver presents when Rudolph gets sick!

title: Birthday Present/Gilbert/Summer Goodnight/Scared of Dogs/The Zoo
description: It's Caillou's birthday and he's having a little party./Caillou has nobody to play with./Caillou just can't get to sleep./Caillou is scared by a stranger's dog./Caillou and his family go to the zoo.

title: Caillou Tries Karate/Just Like Daddy/Caillou's Safari/Cowboy Caillou
description: Leo comes over to play at Caillou's house./Daddy has a list of things to do around the house./Caillou wants to play with his animal cards but they have disappeared./Jonas, a friend of Dad's and a real cowboy, has invited the family to visit his ranch.

title: Shoo, Shoo Bird, Fly Away!/Caillou's Road Trip/Caillou and the Dragon
description: When birds keep eating the seeds in Mommy and Caillou's newly planted garden, they come up with the idea of making a scarecrow./One fine day the family is going on a car trip./There's a special visitor at Caillou's playschool - a boy named Alan who has Down Syndrome.

title: Caillou Bakes a Cake
description: Caillou helps Mommy bake a special cake for Leo's birthday party!

title: Caillou and the Easter Bunny
description: Caillou is excited the Easter Bunny is coming and cannot sleep!

title: Caillou's Horn/The Mighty Oak/Get Well Mr. Hinkle/The Big Boat
description: When Sarah gives Caillou an old toy horn, Caillou wants to blow it everywhere./When Mr. Hinkle has a tree cut down, Caillou is afraid his swing tree is next!/When Caillou dresses up like a mailman to deliver Mr. Hinkle's misdirected mail, he finds out Mr. Hinkle is sick./Caillou and family go on a trip on Helen's boat, an old friend of Mom's.

title: Caillou's Big Slide/Caillou Walks a Dog/Caillou Watches Rosie/Caillou Gets Sick/Caillou's Phone Call
description: Caillou is playing in the park with Clementine./Grandma is looking after her friend's dog again./Mommy isn't feeling well./Caillou has a fever./Mom is busy on the phone all morning.

title: Caillou Helps Out/Caillou the Firefighter/Caillou to the Rescue
description: Rosie is teething and just can't seem to fall asleep./The Fire chief visits Caillou's playschool to teach the children about fire drills./A mischievous Rosie hides Caillou's cars between the cushions on the sofa.

title: Dinosaur Museum
description: Caillou's class takes a field trip to the Museum!

title: Caillou on the Fourth of July
description: Caillou goes to the lake to celebrate the Fourth of July.

title: Three's a Crowd/Get Well Soon/Shadow Play/A New Member of the Family
description: Caillou, Mom and Rosie go the park, where they join Leo and Clementine already playing in the sandbox./Caillou and Leo are having a great time playing spaceman when Leo trips and falls, hurting his foot./After supper one night, Caillou and Jason and Jeffrey decide to play hide and seek in the backyard./Caillou, Mom and Rosie are looking at pictures.

title: Caillou at the Parade
description: Caillou and his family go to see a parade!

title: Caillou the Skateboarder
description: Caillou tries skateboarding again after falling the first time!

title: Caillou's Mini Marathon/Smooth Sailing/Am I Big Yet?
description: Caillou wants to run a marathon, just like Daddy./Caillou likes sailing with Daddy and Grandpa./Rosie has had a growth spurt and Caillou wants one too.

title: Caillou the Knight
description: Caillou faces a fierce dragon that tries to steal his spaghetti!

title: Caillou at the Science Fair
description: Caillou and Leo make an erupting volcano for the science fair!

title: Caillou's Shadow/High Flyers/Caillou's Leaf Pile
description: Caillou likes it when Miss Martin calls him a shadow scientist./Daniel comes for a visit./Caillou has fun jumping in the fall leaves with Daddy.

title: Caillou on World Book Day
description: Caillou chooses a new adventure to read using his free book voucher!

title: A Surprise for Mommy/Caillou Misses Sarah/T-Shirt Trouble/A Helping Hand
description: Dad gets a professional photo of Caillou and Rosie./Caillou's friend Sarah is going away on a trip for two whole weeks./Caillou's brand new T-shirt is ruined by grape juice./Caillou and Grandma, along with Rover the dog, spend a day at a retirement home.

title: Viking Caillou
description: Caillou learns about Vikings at school.

title: Sharing the Rocketship/Coach Granpa/The Safety Helper
description: Caillou and Leo decide to go 'halvsies' on a toy shuttle./Grandpa is coaching Caillou's soccer team./Caillou is very proud when Miss Martin makes him "Safety Helper".

title: Clowning Around/Read All About It/Mom for a Day/Caillou Plays Baseball
description: Caillou visits Grandma who shows him a book about clowns she got from the library./Caillou and Mom go to the library for story time./Caillou helps Daddy look after Rosie./When Caillou notices that Dad and Grandpa are captivated by a baseball game on TV, he wants to get in on the excitement.

title: Caillou the Soccer Player
description: Caillou learns how to work together to make soccer fun!

title: A Sweet and Sour Day/Caillou's Puppet Show/Caillou's Collection
description: Caillou is helping Grandma water her flowers and fill the birdbath./Caillou and his friends Jason and Jeffrey make finger puppets at playschool and decide to put on a puppet show./In the park Caillou starts a new hobby - collecting rocks!

title: Where I Live/A Good Friend/Just Like Me/Just In Time/Mr. Fixit
description: When an invitation for Clementine's party accidentally ends up at Sarah's, Caillou learns the differences between the addresses of the two homes./When Leo forgets his brand new toy dinosaur in the park, Daddy and Caillou go looking for it./When Clementine tells Caillou how much she likes her older brother, Billy, to teach her things, Caillou sets out to teach something to Rosie./When Caillou's dawdling causes he, Mom and Rosie to be late going to the park, they end up missing Leo./When the washing machine needs fixing, Caillou ends up helping Bob the repairman.

title: Caillou the Prankster
description: When Caillou tries out some of Leo's prank toys, his family is in for a surprise!

title: Caillou at the Pool
description: Caillou has fun while staying safe at the pool, and tries out the big water slide!

title: Caillou Goes Caroling/A Playschool Party/Caillou's Christmas Eve
description: Caillou goes out caroling for the very first time with Mommy, Daddy, Rosie, Grandpa and Grandma./It's a very special day at playschool as they celebrate the many ways of celebrating the holiday season./It's finally Christmas Eve and Caillou just can't wait for nighttime.

title: Caillou of the Future
description: Caillou and Daddy play a VR video game at the arcade and try to win a prize.

title: Caillou's Song/Follow Me/Where's Caillou?
description: Caillou wants to learn to play a song on his little keyboard./Caillou tries to befriend his new classmate, Andy./Caillou wants someone to play with.

title: Looks for Gilbert/Surprise Breakfast/Missing Sock/Goes to Work/Quarrel
description: Caillou is having a game of dinosaur hunter with Gilbert the cat./Caillou gets up early one morning./Caillou wants to wear his favorite socks, but one of them is missing./Caillou goes to work with Mom./Clementine comes over to play.

title: Show and Tell/Caillou the Magician/Caillou's Castle
description: Caillou has to decide on a nice surprise to bring to playschool for Show and Tell./Grandma shows Caillou a simple magic trick, which makes him decide to be a magician./Caillou wants to play castles and dragons, even though Gilbert isn't very keen on playing the dragon.

title: Caillou's Explorer Adventure
description: Caillou and friends come up with an adventurous plan to save Teddy from Cavegirl Rosie!

title: Caillou of the Antarctic/Deep Sea Caillou/Caillou in the Bayou
description: Caillou is playing with Jeffrey and Jason when he gets accidentally pushed down./There's a new girl named Lee Wun in playschool, but she's so shy she won't talk to anybody./The whole family is on the way to the beach but accidentally ends up on a trail through a swamp.

title: Where's Mars?/Emma's Extra Snacks/Lost and Found
description: Caillou and Daddy are finishing up a model of the solar system./Caillou is confused when Emma is allowed to have extra snacks./When things begin to go missing around the house Mommy blames Gilbert.
